Class RecommenderJColibri

  • java.lang.Object

    public class RecommenderJColibri
extends Object
implements RecommenderAlgorithm, es.ucm.fdi.gaia.jcolibri.cbraplications.StandardCBRApplication
    Class that implements a content-based recommender algorithm using jCOLIBRI framework. In this class is necessary inject the connector (is the knowledge source of the recommender system).
